messages.text: Please be alive. Please please please
I didn’t mean to drag you into this
I’m fine. About to pass out, but fine. Thank you for ASKING.
Yeah. Well. I got your stupid tablet.
Now I’m chilling here in some shrubbery till I figure out
Calm down. It’ll be okay. Can you tell me what happened??
I was hiding behind the Prof’s desk in the lab
And some woman with a GUN
Was about to check behind the desk
And I was like OH GOD
Dunno. Not like I had time to inquire.
Red hair. Real pissed off. I didn’t recognize her.
But she had this look like she knew me or something
Anyway, can you open the tablet?
Log in and try to access Stella’s A.I. before it freaks out and ...
That crazy redheaded lady followed me!
I did not sign up for this!
2) being chased by a crazy lady with a gun, and
3) The lethal combination of the two.
It’s going to be alright. I promise.
Holed up in the library stacks
Hiding in the one place no one will look.
Encyclopedias! When was the last time you used a hard copy encyclopedia?
That frat dude Tucker is calling.
If he connects the dots, I’m toast.
U tell me, K-Dawg. Just saw u running across campus.
Oh, that was merely a spirited constitutional.
You know I love physical fitness!
Yeah, I don’t buy that, son.
I dunno what’s going on but you’ve been acting real suspicious.
U know there was a break-in at the Prof’s lab?
I saw u there right before it happened.
Excuse me. You’re suggesting I broke into the Prof’s lab?
Naw, didn’t say that bro. I just think it’s a funny coincidence.
Your girlfriend Lucy steals that car.
And now security is reporting that there’s an armed woman on campus.
Hold up. Where was she last spotted?
1) For the first time in his life…
Tucker is using his brain, but even worse…
2) The redhead was spotted near the library
I see your location on the map
Can u hack into Stella’s GPS?
Whew! Now we can set Stella’s next destination
Set course for the big park outside campus
Kam, we need a secluded place to review the tablet
And campus isn’t safe as long as that redhead psycho is on the loose.
Exactly. Meet you there in an hour...
Have you watched any scary movies ever?
FACT. Shady things happen in parks after dark.
It’s the only way to stop the Prof’s research from falling into the wrong hands
Once you find out what he was working on
Please Kam ... do this for me
Soon we can put this whole thing behind us and go on that date.
Think about it. You. Me. Dumplings.
Setting Stella’s GPS for the park.
It’s working! Stella is turning around!
I’m sure you’d do the same for me.
I’ll see you at the park in an hour
I don’t think it’s an accident.
Not risking it. I gotta book it out of this library.
Just gotta get down this stairwell.
Which, looks a lot like an abyss of murder.
Lucy, I’m so sick of this creepy adventure stuff
I know you’re up there, Kam.
I knew that question was asking for trouble.
